Titolo: Light Crusader

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Light Crusader is an action-adventure game developed by Treasure and published by Sega for their Sega Genesis console in 1995. The game was included in the Sega Genesis Classics collections on Steam and other platforms in 2010. It was also included on the Sega Genesis Mini in North America and Sega Mega Drive Mini in PAL regions.
It is similar in gameplay to Landstalker, blending role-playing video game, action-adventure and platform video game elements in much the same way.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
